ed="T" n="0849c13"/><persName key="A012883">釋如敏</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000017165">閩</placeName>人也。始見<persName key="A003636">安<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，遂盛化嶺外，<lb
ed="T" n="0849c14"/>誠多異迹。其為人也，寬綽純篤，無故寡言，<lb
ed="T" n="0849c15"/>深憫迷愚，率行激勸。<persName key="A006590">劉<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>偏覇<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>，每迎<lb
ed="T" n="0849c16"/>召<persName key="A012883">敏</persName>入請問，多逆知其來，驗同合契。廣主<lb
ed="T" n="0849c17"/>奕世<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1828"/>奉以周旋，時時禮見，有疑不決，直往詢<lb
ed="T" n="0849c18"/>訪<ptr target="#n2795"/>。<persName key="A012883">敏</persName>亦無嫌忌，啟發口占，然皆准的，時謂之<lb
ed="T" n="0849c19"/>為乞願，乃私署為<persName key="A012883">知聖大師</persName>。初<persName key="A012883">敏</persName>以一苦<lb
ed="T" n="0849c20"/>行為侍者，頗副心意，呼之曰<persName key="A019460">所由</persName>也。一<lb
ed="T" n="0849c21"/>日，隨登山脊間却之，潛令下山，迴顧見<persName key="A012883">敏</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0849c22"/>入地焉。<ref type="person" target="#A019460">苦行</ref>隱草中覆其形，久伺之乃出，<lb
ed="T" n="0849c23"/>往迎之，問曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012883">師</ref>焉往乎？」曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012883">吾</ref>與山王有舊，<lb
ed="T" n="0849c24"/>邀命言話來。」如是時或亡者，乃穴地而出。嚴<lb
ed="T" n="0849c25"/>誡之曰：「<persName key="A019460">所由</persName>無宜外說，洩<ref type="person" target="#A012883">吾</ref>閑務。」後終于<lb
ed="T" n="0849c26"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000030549">住院</ref>，全身不散。喪塔官供，今號<placeName key="PL000000059384">靈樹禪師<lb
ed="T" n="0849c27"/>真身塔</placeName>，是歟！</p><p xml:id="pT50p0849c2801"><lb
ed="T" n="0849c28"/>系曰：<persName key="A012883">靈樹</persName>如遇<persName key="A003636">大安</persName>，必壽臘綿長，出人常<lb
ed="T" n="0849c29"/>限。疑此亦所聞異辭矣。<ptr target="#n2796"/></p>
